data.description: NEW CONSTRUCTION, mobile home on almost one acre in Southern Wakulla County!  Move in ready! This wonderful Clayton manufactured home features an open floor plan concept with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, kitchen with an island and custom cabinetry, large bedrooms with nice size closets, spacious master bath and utility room. No carpet! This home also offers an outside barn! If you are looking for a private homestead, this one awaits you!
